snippet.title: 10 Things You Didn't Know About AMBER HEARD!
snippet.description:
10 Things You Didn't Know About AMBER HEARD!

Join us in today’s video as we show you 10 things you never knew about Amber Heard. When it comes to Hollywood blondes, Amber Heard is among the most essential. As an actress, a model, a LGTBQ activist, and ex-partner to some of the most eccentric figures in the world, Heard’s personal life rivals her filmography—at least in terms of public interest.

Although not a singer, Heard makes sure her voice is heard when she talks about social issues in the industry. She’s worked in horror movies, drama thrillers, and even TV; although some of these projects weren’t exactly “blockbusters,” these roles show that Heard has the experience to back up her opinions. But there’s more to Amber than what most people know her for. Be sure to watch the whole video and see who Amber Heard really is! In addition, do us a favor and like the video and subscribe and turn on the notification bell. We’ll see you in the next video!
